@host = http://localhost:5062

### Liveness probe (nssm uses this)
GET {{host}}/health
Accept: application/json

###

### List known projects (from <repo>/projects.json)
GET {{host}}/projects
Accept: application/json

###

### List available flows (cli/flows/*.cs minus smoke-*)
GET {{host}}/flows
Accept: application/json

###

### Start a run
POST {{host}}/runs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "project": "card-framework",
  "flow":    "claude-only",
  "prompt":  "list the files in the project directory",
  "args":    []
}

###

### List runs (most recent first)
GET {{host}}/runs
Accept: application/json

###

### Get one run
GET {{host}}/runs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000
Accept: application/json

###

### Cancel a run
POST {{host}}/runs/00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000/cancel
